data.description: Nestled within the charming community of South Oak, this stunning 2-story colonial brick pool home with a detached Guest House is a rare gem. Boasting 5 bedrooms, 4.5 bathrooms, and a generous 3,176 Sq Ft Main House and 1,404 Sq Ft  Guest House space, this residence sits on just under 1 acre of lush surroundings in an established neighborhood with no CDD, low HOA, featuring only 84 custom homes.    The inviting foyer with soaring ceilings and a beautiful spiral staircase leads to the Living room with wood floors and a stunning tiled wainscoting.  Step into the Kitchen showcasing custom wood cabinetry, large cooktop island with an additional prep sink,  a built-in work space, large windows adorned with Plantation Shutters are the backdrop for the eat-in alcove, new stainless steel appliances and Corian counters really makes this a WOW Kitchen! The large Family Room has tray ceiling, a fireplace, wet bar and access to the enclosed 514 Sq Ft brick porch climate controlled with a dedicated A/C Unit. Two office/study/den spaces with impressive built-in shelving and brick-style wood floors add versatility to the first floor layout. An elevator provides access to the second level and the Primary Bedroom featuring a tray ceiling, 2 walk-in closets, ensuite bathroom with jetted soaking tub, glass shower, 2 separate vanities, and water closet for privacy.  This Primary suite also has access to a catwalk spanning the front entrance with built-in shelving and a cozy reading nook.  3 secondary bedrooms, and a full bathroom complete the second level.  The backyard is a shady oasis with a screened lap pool, fenced yard with a wooden swing set, long driveway leading to an attached 3 car side entry garage and a detached brick Guest House and brick walkways and patio with gazebo and outdoor kitchen.     The detached Guest House is 1 bed/1 bath, 1,404 Sq Ft, has 2 private entrances, dedicated parking, a 21x12’ bedroom with a 14x5’ walk-in closet, family/kitchen combination, living room, bathroom with accessible shower, and a 22x13’ flex space for garage or bonus room with laundry and attic storage including an electronic lift, 2 dedicated A/C Units, and an 8kw generator for power outages.    FEATURES:  Elevator in main house. Roof replaced 2021. Updated Stainless Steel Kitchen Appliances (fridge in 2022 and double oven in 2023). Parking pad for RV with electric and water.  Wooden play-set. Lap Pool with screen enclosure. Foyer chandelier with switch to lower for light bulb replacement. Tankless Water Heaters. Double insulated windows and sliding doors with adjustable blinds encased.  Schedule your showing today! All sizes are approximate and please verify.
